quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"And as soon as the son of Maryam (levity (Son of Mary, ) is struck as a similitude, only then have your people clamored aloud thereat"
  43,58,"And they have said, \"Are our gods more charitable, or rather he? In no way have they struck (the similitude) to you except in dispute; no indeed, (but) they are a people, (who are) constant adversaries"
  43,59,"Decidedly he is nothing except a bondman We favored, and We made him to be a similitude to the Seeds (Or: sons) of Israel"
  43,60,"And if We had (so) decided, We would indeed have made from among you Angels to be successors in the earth"
  43,61,"And surely it is indeed knowledge of the Hour; so definitely do not wrangle about it, and closely follow Me. This is a straight Path"
  43,62,"And definitely do not let Shaytan (The) ever-vicious (one), i.e., the Devil) bar you; (i.e., the believers) surely he is for you an evident enemy"
  43,63,"And as soon as Isa (Jesus) came with the supreme evidence (s), he said, \"I have readily come to you with (the) Wisdom, and that I may make evident to you some of that concerning which you differ; so be pious to Allah, and obey me"
  43,64,"Surely Allah, Ever He, is my Lord and your Lord; so worship Him. This is a straight Path"
  43,65,Yet the (allied) parties differed among themselves; so woe to the ones who did injustice from the torment of a painful Day
  43,66,"Are they looking for (anything) except the Hour, that it will come to them suddenly, when they are not aware"
  43,67,"Close fellows upon that Day will be enemies to one another, (Literally: some of them to some (others) except the pious"